CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Blue Water Vaccines Inc is a biotechnology company focused on the research and development of transformational vaccines to prevent infectious diseases. Its versatile vaccine platform has molecular properties that enable delivery of various antigens, which can be utilized to develop singular or multi-targeted vaccines.
